        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 3. Plantar views of left forefoot (manus) and wrist of Marmosops pinheiroi (A, AMNH 267346) and M. bishopi (B, MUSM 23801) illustrating different morphologies of the lateral carpal tubercle (lct), which is spoon shaped in adult males of M. pinheiroi and bladelike (laterally compressed) in adult males of M. bishopi." ;
