<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4612638>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 8. Lingual view of the first two lower right molars (m1 and m2) of Marmosops bishopi (A, AMNH 276697) and M. carri (B, AMNH 234953) illustrating taxonomic differences in the cusp height. In M. bishopi the entoconid (encd) of m1 is shorter than the adjacent paraconid (pacd) of m2, whereas these cusps are subequal in height in M. carri." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4612638/files/figure.png" .
